 </td>
 <td align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#600000">
  <font size="3" face="Verdana">
  <a href="types.htm">Different types of PONG systems</a><br><br>
  They all play the same games but use different technologies.
  This article explains the technologies used in PONG systems: analog, digital,
  integrated, and programmed.</font>
 </td>
</tr>

