  <a href="peritel.htm">How to connect a PONG system to the composite video input 
  or your TV set</a><br><br>
  A solution to the common problem of modern television sets which don't always work with
  the unstable video signals of old PONG systems. Beware: this solution requires technical
  skills and does not work with every PONG system.</font>
